item.description:
Readers can be attached one or more Lambda functions and processes the CloudWatch logs the functions produce. Log messages can be filtered to reduce message volume.
To create a log reader, call the Reader() method on a service builder.
// Create a reader for logs containing the word &quot;error&quot; onErrors := service.Reader(&quot;on-errors&quot;, func(ctx context.Context, evt events.CloudwatchLogsEvent) error { // ... }) // Create some Lambda functions processor := service.Processor(...) observer := service.
